data.description: WHAT A LOCATION! This home sits on a very large lot on one of the most sought after streets in Keokuk. This 3 bedroom 2 and a half bath home has been given a brand new look with all new exterior paint and a landscaping overhaul. The extra large living room and dining room was just modernized with a fresh coat of paint. Key features of the interior of the home are an extra large living space, master bedroom with adjoining bathroom, walk in closet, and a large 2nd closet. Most of the windows have been replaced, new luxury vinyl flooring, new toilets in all 3 bathrooms, updated kitchen, and nearly 2000 sq ft of basement space. All the big expenses have been taken care of, with a newer roof, hot water heater, furnace, and air conditioner. This is a must see!
